  "title": "Executive Assistant/ Personal Assistant (Entry/ Junior Level) |Basic up $3500, 5 days, Central [R22107578]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Basic Salary up to $3500</li><li>5 days work week (Monday - Friday)</li><li>Location: Central</li><li>Career Progression Opportunities</li><li>Report to director</li></ul></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide comprehensive administrative and secretarial support, including managing schedules, travel arrangements, and meetings.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and organize business documents such as reports, presentations, correspondence, and itineraries.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate and support meetings by preparing agendas, taking minutes, and tracking follow-up actions.</p></li><li><p>Liaise with internal teams, clients, and external partners to facilitate communication and document management.</p></li><li><p>Assist in processing insurance-related tasks, including claims, policy updates, and maintaining accurate records.</p></li><li><p>Create professional presentations, reports, and marketing materials using design tools while maintaining brand consistency.</p></li><li><p>Support team operations, compliance, and onboarding of new staff through training and process improvement initiatives.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma in Business Administration, or any other field</p></li><li><p>At least 1 year of personal assistant experience<br /></p></li></ul><p>To Apply, kindly click on the \"APPLY NOW\" button and job details.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>StaffKing Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Jasmine Wong (R22107578)</p>",
